eement with spectroscopic survey\nresults. In the co-rotating frame, we find evidence of bar-supporting x1 orbits\nand tangential bias in the in-plane dispersion field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Mar 2019 19:00:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-10"}
