mic approach that avoids\nthe integrations of the Bluman-Kumei approach where MapDE can determine if a\nlinear differential equation R can be mapped to a linear constant coefficient\ndifferential equation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Mar 2019 05:32:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-07"}
