cture of BLG has an important\ninfluence on Li diffusion within BLG, and changing the stacking structure of\nBLG is one possible way to greatly improve Li diffusion rate within BLG. At\nlast, it is suggested that AB-stacked BLG can be an excellent candidate for\nanode material in Lithium-ion batteries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Mar 2019 06:54:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-10"}
